# E-Commerce-website
A one-page e-commerce website for desktop presents products in a single, scrollable layout. It features clear visuals, product details, and an easy checkout process. This design improves user experience by simplifying navigation, reducing steps, and helping customers quickly explore, select, and purchase items efficiently on larger screens.
